#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.corr.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.corr"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:1 of
msgid "Compute pairwise correlation of columns, excluding NA/null values."
msgstr "计算列之间的成对相关性，排除 NA/null 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:3 of
msgid ""
"Method of correlation:  * pearson : standard correlation coefficient * "
"kendall : Kendall Tau correlation coefficient * spearman : Spearman rank "
"correlation * callable: callable with input two 1d ndarrays     and "
"returning a float. Note that the returned matrix from corr     will have "
"1 along the diagonals and will be symmetric     regardless of the "
"callable's behavior.  .. note::     kendall, spearman and callables not "
"supported on multiple chunks yet."
msgstr ""
"相关性方法：  * pearson : 标准相关系数 * kendall : Kendall Tau 相关系数 *"
" spearman : Spearman 秩相关 * callable: 输入为两个一维 ndarray 并返回一个"
"浮点数的可调用对象。注意，从 corr 返回的矩阵将在对角线上为 1，并且无论可"
"调用对象的行为如何，矩阵都是对称的。  .. note::     尚不支持在多个块上"
"使用 kendall、spearman 和 callable。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:3 of
msgid "Method of correlation:"
msgstr "相关性方法："

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:5 of
msgid "pearson : standard correlation coefficient"
msgstr "pearson : 标准相关系数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:6 of
msgid "kendall : Kendall Tau correlation coefficient"
msgstr "kendall : Kendall Tau 相关系数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:7 of
msgid "spearman : Spearman rank correlation"
msgstr "spearman : Spearman 秩相关"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:8 of
msgid "callable: callable with input two 1d ndarrays"
msgstr "callable: 接受两个一维ndarray作为输入的可调用对象"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:9 of
msgid ""
"and returning a float. Note that the returned matrix from corr will have "
"1 along the diagonals and will be symmetric regardless of the callable's "
"behavior."
msgstr ""
"并返回一个浮点数。注意，corr返回的矩阵对角线上的值将为1，并且无论可调用"
"对象的行为如何，矩阵都是对称的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:14 of
msgid "kendall, spearman and callables not supported on multiple chunks yet."
msgstr "kendall、spearman和可调用对象目前还不支持多个分块。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:16 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations required per pair of columns to have a "
"valid result. Currently only available for Pearson and Spearman "
"correlation."
msgstr ""
"每对列需要的最小观测数量以获得有效结果。目前仅适用于 Pearson 和 Spearman "
"相关性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:21 of
msgid "Correlation matrix."
msgstr "相关性矩阵。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.corrwith`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:27 of
msgid "Compute pairwise correlation with another DataFrame or Series."
msgstr "与另一个 DataFrame 或 Series 计算成对相关性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.corr`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corr:30 of
msgid "Compute the correlation between two Series."
msgstr "计算两个 Series 之间的相关性。"

